text: Kingdom in the Clouds (Romanian: Tinerețe fără bătrânețe – literal title: Youth Without Old Age) is a 1969 Romanian Russian fantasy movie directed by Elisabeta Bostan and starring Carmen Stănescu, Nicolae Secăreanu, Emanoil Petruț, Anna Széles, Mircea Breazu, Ioan Tugearu. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1969 movies Category:1960s fantasy movies Category:Romanian movies Category:Russian fantasy movies Category:Movies directed by Elisabeta Bostan
